PW Medtech Group Ltd.


            
            PW Medtech Group Ltd. is an investment holding company, which engages in the production of medical devices. It operates through the following business segments: Infusion Set, Orthopedic Implant, and Regenerative Medical Biomaterial. The Infusion Sets segment produces non-polyvinyl chloride, precision filter, and light resistant infusion sets. The Orthopedic Implant segment manufactures and sells trauma, spine, and joints products. The Regenerative Medical Biomaterial segment comprises of DuraMax, DuraGide, Artificial Nerve, and medical cosmetic-grade skin treatment mask. The company was founded on May 13, 2011 and is headquartered in Beijing, China.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  




